            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Hd1e108">Rubrica 22</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De vsurarum prohibitione religiosa et morali</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>¶ De vsurarum prohibitione re
      <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>ligiosa et morali. Rubrica. 22
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="56"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Rd1e118">MOises. in deuterono. c. 23</ref>
      <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Qd1e127">Non feneraberi 
               fra<lb ed="#V" n="58" break="no"/>tri tuo ad vsuram pecuniam nec 
               fru<lb ed="#V" n="59" break="no"/>ges nec aliam quamlibet rem sed alieno</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-d1e142">
               <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Qd1e146">/ Fratri tuo absque vsura id quod indiget como
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>dabis: vt benedicat tibi dominus deus tuus in opere tuo</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-d1e152">
               <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Rd1e145">Ezechiel propheta. c. 18.</ref>  <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Qd1e156">Ad vsuram dantem
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>et amplius accipientem numquid viuet:</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-d1e162">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Rd1e157">Socrates in exhortationibus. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Qd1e166">
               Absti<lb ed="#V" n="65" break="no"/>nentiam exerceas fenoris</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-d1e172">
               <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Rd1e169">Aristoteles ethicorum: li. 4. c. 2.</ref>  <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Qd1e176">Usurarii vne
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>non oportet accipiunt et quantum non oportet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-d1e182">
               <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Rd1e181">Iesus filius syrach in ecclesiastico. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Qd1e186">Noli 
               fe<lb ed="#V" n="69" break="no"/>nerari omni fortiori te.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-d1e192"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Rd1e191">29. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Qd1e194"> Qui facit misericordiam
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>feneratur proximo suo.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-d1e201"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Qd1e203">Fenerare proximo tibi
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>in tempore necessitatis illius.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-d1e209"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Qd1e211">Multi non causa 
               nequi<lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>tie fenerati sunt: sed fraudari gratis timuerunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-d1e217">
               <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Rd1e220">Lucas in euange. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Qd1e221">Si mutuum dederitis
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>his a quibus speratis recipere qua vobis est gratia:</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-d1e227">
               <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de6152-Qd1e231">/ Mutuum date nihil inde sperantes: et erit 
               mer<lb ed="#V" n="76" break="no"/>ces vestra multa: et eritis filii altissimi: quia ipse
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>benignus est super ingratos et malos.</quote>
            </p>
